wiki.content:
This is the lead single of the "Hannah Montana: The Movie" soundtrack, released on March 24, 2009. It is performed by Golden Globe nominee, Miley Cyrus. This song was written by Jessi Alexander and Jon Mabe. About "The Climb" To your dreams.
